ActMackenzie Valley Resource Management Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Mackenzie Valley Land Use Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the MACKENZIE VALLEY LAND USE REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) correct certain typographical errors in the Regulations; and (2) remove an illegal fee calculation rule in the application form contained in Schedule 2 of the English and French versions of the Regulations.
